        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-ambient"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-eyebrow">
          <span class="badge badge-available">Available now</span>
          <span class="badge-text">MCP Server for Claude & AI Agents</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Stop editing Word documents.<br/>
          <span class="hero-highlight">Let AI do it.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-description">
          Your team spends hours formatting reports, updating contracts, and fixing documents manually.
          docx-mcp connects your AI assistants directly to Microsoft Word — so they can read, edit, and format documents for you.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
            Get Started Free
          </a>
          <a href="#products" class="btn btn-secondary">See the Roadmap</a>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-proof">
          <div class="proof-item">
            <span class="proof-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Works with Claude Desktop</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-item">
            <span class="proof-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>Open Source</span>
          </div>
          <div class="proof-item">
            <span class="proof-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span>MIT License</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="visual-card">
          <div class="visual-header">
            <div class="visual-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
            <span class="visual-title">Claude</span>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-content">
            <div class="chat-message user">
              <p>"Update the Q4 report with new sales figures and format the executive summary."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="chat-message assistant">
              <p>Done! I've updated the sales figures in all 12 tables and reformatted the executive summary with the new highlights. The document is saved.</p>
              <div class="chat-file">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="16" height="16"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="2"/></svg>
                Q4-Report-2024.docx
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem Section -->
  <section class="problem">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="problem-content">
        <h2>Document editing is still manual. In 2024.</h2>
        <p>
          AI can write code, analyze data, and answer complex questions.
          But when it comes to your Word documents? You're still copying, pasting, and formatting by hand.
        </p>
        <div class="problem-stats">
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">5h+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">per week spent on document formatting</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span class="stat-number">73%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">of knowledge workers edit docs daily</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Products Section -->
  <section id="products" class="products">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The docx-mcp Ecosystem</h2>
        <p>One mission: make document editing automatic. Multiple products to get there.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="products-grid">
        <!-- Available Now -->
        <div class="product-card product-available">
          <div class="product-status">
            <span class="status-dot available"></span>
            Available now
          </div>
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="8" y="4" width="32" height="40" rx="4" fill="#0078d4"/>
              <path d="M16 16h16M16 24h16M16 32h10" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>MCP Server</h3>
          <p>
            Connect Claude, Cursor, or any MCP-compatible AI to your Word documents.
            Read, edit, format — all through natural language.
          </p>
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp" class="product-link" target="_blank">
            View on GitHub
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="16" height="16"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Coming Soon Products -->
        <div class="product-card product-coming">
          <div class="product-status">
            <span class="status-dot coming"></span>
            Coming soon
          </div>
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="6" y="8" width="36" height="32" rx="4" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="8" fill="#0078d4"/>
              <path d="M24 20v4l3 3" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Word Add-in</h3>
          <p>
            AI-powered editing directly inside Microsoft Word.
            Available for Windows, macOS, and iPad.
          </p>
          <div class="product-platforms">
            <span>Windows</span>
            <span>macOS</span>
            <span>iPad</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card product-coming">
          <div class="product-status">
            <span class="status-dot coming"></span>
            Coming soon
          </div>
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M24 4L6 14v20l18 10 18-10V14L24 4z" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="2"/>
              <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="6" fill="#0078d4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Claude Skill</h3>
          <p>
            Use docx-mcp capabilities directly in Claude.ai.
            No setup, no installation — just ask Claude to edit your documents.
          </p>
          <div class="product-badge">Anthropic Partnership</div>
        </div>

        <div class="product-card product-coming product-wide">
          <div class="product-status">
            <span class="status-dot coming"></span>
            Coming soon
          </div>
          <div class="product-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path d="M8 24h8l4-8 4 16 4-8h12" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <circle cx="8" cy="24" r="3" fill="#0078d4"/>
              <circle cx="40" cy="24" r="3" fill="#0078d4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Agentic Document Workflows</h3>
          <p>
            End-to-end automation for enterprise document pipelines.
            Connect your documents to AI agents that handle the entire editing lifecycle — from draft to final approval.
          </p>
          <div class="product-integrations">
            <div class="integration">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24"><path d="M21.007 8.222A3.738 3.738 0 0 0 17.227 5.5a3.727 3.727 0 0 0-2.69 1.157 5.452 5.452 0 0 0-2.532-.643 5.477 5.477 0 0 0-5.476 5.477v.057a3.738 3.738 0 0 0 .643 7.447h10.855a3.738 3.738 0 0 0 2.98-5.773z"/></svg>
              <span>Microsoft 365</span>
            </div>
            <div class="integration">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12.5 2h-9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-9a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5zm7 7h-4a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5 1.5v10a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h4a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5v-10a1.5 1.5 0 0 0-1.5-1.5z"/></svg>
              <span>SharePoint</span>
            </div>
            <div class="integration">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
              <span>Amazon S3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="integration">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24"><path d="M22.46 6c-.77.35-1.6.58-2.46.69.88-.53 1.56-1.37 1.88-2.38-.83.5-1.75.85-2.72 1.05C18.37 4.5 17.26 4 16 4c-2.35 0-4.27 1.92-4.27 4.29 0 .34.04.67.11.98C8.28 9.09 5.11 7.38 3 4.79c-.37.63-.58 1.37-.58 2.15 0 1.49.75 2.81 1.91 3.56-.71 0-1.37-.2-1.95-.5v.03c0 2.08 1.48 3.82 3.44 4.21a4.22 4.22 0 0 1-1.93.07 4.28 4.28 0 0 0 4 2.98 8.521 8.521 0 0 1-5.33 1.84c-.34 0-.68-.02-1.02-.06C3.44 20.29 5.7 21 8.12 21 16 21 20.33 14.46 20.33 8.79c0-.19 0-.37-.01-.56.84-.6 1.56-1.36 2.14-2.23z"/></svg>
              <span>ChatGPT</span>
            </div>
            <div class="integration">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 10 10A10 10 0 0 0 12 2zm0 18a8 8 0 1 1 8-8 8 8 0 0 1-8 8z"/><path d="M12 6a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v5a1 1 0 0 0 .29.71l3 3a1 1 0 0 0 1.42-1.42L13 11.59V7a1 1 0 0 0-1-1z"/></svg>
              <span>Claude</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <section id="vision" class="vision">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="vision-content">
        <h2>The future of document editing is agentic</h2>
        <p>
          We're building toward a world where you never manually edit a Word document again.
          Your AI assistant understands your intent, knows your documents, and handles the formatting,
          updates, and revisions — while you focus on what matters.
        </p>
        <div class="vision-features">
          <div class="vision-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <h4>Multi-platform</h4>
              <p>Works everywhere your documents live — Microsoft 365, SharePoint, local files, cloud storage.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M12 1v6m0 6v10M1 12h6m6 0h10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <h4>AI-native</h4>
              <p>Built for Claude, ChatGPT, and the next generation of AI assistants.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="vision-feature">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-text">
              <h4>Enterprise-ready</h4>
              <p>Security, compliance, and audit trails built in from day one.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Ready to automate your document workflows?</h2>
        <p>Start with the open-source MCP Server today. Be first in line for what's next.</p>
        <div class="cta-actions">
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp" class="btn btn-primary btn-large" target="_blank">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
            Get Started on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="cta-note">Free and open source under MIT License</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Doccy - The AI Document Assistant (inspired by a certain paperclip) -->
  <div class="doccy-container" id="doccy">
    <div class="doccy-bubble" id="doccy-bubble">
      <button class="doccy-close" id="doccy-close" aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
      <p id="doccy-message">Hi! I'm Doccy. It looks like you're trying to edit a Word document. Would you like AI to do it for you?</p>
      <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp" class="doccy-btn" target="_blank">Yes, show me how!</a>
    </div>
    <div class="doccy-character" id="doccy-character">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 100 160" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="doccy-svg">
        <!-- Paperclip body -->
        <path
          d="M30 140 L30 40 Q30 15 50 15 Q70 15 70 40 L70 120 Q70 135 55 135 Q40 135 40 120 L40 50 Q40 40 50 40 Q60 40 60 50 L60 100"
          stroke="#0078d4"
          stroke-width="8"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          fill="none"
          class="doccy-body"
        />
        <!-- Left eye -->
        <ellipse cx="42" cy="55" rx="8" ry="10" fill="white" class="doccy-eye-bg"/>
        <ellipse cx="44" cy="57" rx="4" ry="5" fill="#1a1a1a" class="doccy-pupil doccy-pupil-left"/>
        <!-- Right eye -->
        <ellipse cx="58" cy="55" rx="8" ry="10" fill="white" class="doccy-eye-bg"/>
        <ellipse cx="60" cy="57" rx="4" ry="5" fill="#1a1a1a" class="doccy-pupil doccy-pupil-right"/>
        <!-- Eyebrows -->
        <path d="M34 45 Q42 42 50 45" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" class="doccy-brow"/>
        <path d="M50 45 Q58 42 66 45" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" class="doccy-brow"/>
        <!-- Smile -->
        <path d="M42 72 Q50 82 58 72" stroke="#0078d4" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none" class="doccy-smile"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-content">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <div class="logo">
            <div class="logo-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <rect x="3" y="2" width="14" height="18" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
                <path d="M7 7h6M7 11h6M7 15h4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <circle cx="18" cy="18" r="5" fill="#0078d4"/>
                <path d="M16 18h4M18 16v4" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <span>docx-mcp</span>
          </div>
          <p>AI-powered document editing for everyone.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp/issues" target="_blank">Issues</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/valdo404/docx-mcp/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank">MIT License</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Container */
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--spacing-xxl);
  }

  /* Navigation */
  .nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .nav-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--spacing-l) var(--spacing-xxl);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-s);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    font-size: var(--font-size-400);
  }

  .logo:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .logo-icon {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .logo-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-xxl);
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--font-size-300);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-github {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--spacing-s);
    padding: var(--spacing-m) var(--spacing-xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-s);
    font-size: var(--font-size-300);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--brand-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--brand-primary-hover);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-default);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--bg-layer-3);
    border-color: var(--border-strong);
  }

  .btn-large {
    padding: var(--spacing-l) var(--spacing-xxl);
    font-size: var(--font-size-400);
  }

  /* Hero Section */
